title: Exercise: Viewing the Results of a Workflow

questions.question: If you were already inspecting one dataset in FME Data Inspector and wished to add another to your current View, which button would you use?
Why does the JSON format data not appear as a text file in FME Data Inspector?
options: FME Data Inspector always displays features and their associated attributes in a Feature Information, Graphics, or Table view.
JSON cannot be displayed as a plain text file.
